	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm completely new to the world of NES assembly programming, and haven't found a good place to start. None of the tutorials I've seen are very newbie friendly, or so outdated that none of the corresponding files can still be obtained.
<br />
<br />Does anyone know of a good tutorial for someone like to could use to start learning about NES programming?
<br />
<br />thanks!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


